  "text": "This study was carried out in strict accordance with the recommendations in the Guide for the Care and Use of Laboratory Animals of the National Institutes of Health. The protocol was approved by the Animal Care and Use Committee of the Northwestern University (Protocol number: IS00000985). , and Qa-1 +/+ littermates [CITATION_1] . All mice were housed in a specific pathogen free environment at Northwestern University.",
